T*
(Risks / Open Questions) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(    1. The label FOLD in 357 may be misleading because it is implemented as STAY.) Tj
T*
(    2. If the desired design is truly only GO/STAY in 357, the extra FOLD button may need) Tj
T*
(      removal or relabeling.) Tj
T*
(    3. If the desired design is true 357 folding, the engine must be changed to record FOLD) Tj
