(Fold/Check/Raise have not replaced GO/STAY globally. The application currently has separate) Tj
T*
(  357 and standard-poker control systems. In 357, GO/STAY are the real game decisions and FOLD) Tj
T*
(  is currently treated as STAY. In standard Hold'em-style play, Fold/Check/Raise are real) Tj
T*
(  betting actions and are enforced by the engine.) Tj
